com.interpss.core.dclf
Interface DclfAlgorithm

All Superinterfaces:
AclfNetworkRef, DcLoadflow, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAreaTDFactor, IBranchAngleShiftFactor, IDclfResult, ILineOutageDFactor, ILossFactor, INative, IPowerTDFactor, ISensitivity, NameTag, NetworkRef, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
DclfAlgorithmImpl
public interface DclfAlgorithm
extends DcLoadflow, ISensitivity, IPowerTDFactor, IAreaTDFactor, ILossFactor, ILineOutageDFactor, IBranchAngleShiftFactor

A representation of the model object 'Algorithm'.

The following features are supported:

  • Inject Bus Type
  • Withdraw Bus Type
  • Lodf Analysis Type
  • Withdraw Bus List
  • Inject Bus List
  • Outage Branch List
